high_descs: Cross the room between the back of the couch and the table, then face the black table with the yellow lamp on it.
Pick up the closest red credit card to you from on the table.
Turn to your right and go between the dining table and the wall, then face the table.
Put the credit card in the gray bowl on the table.
Pick up the bowl from the table top.
Bring the bowl with you and turn left and make your way around the couch, move to face the coffee table.
Put the bowl down on the table to the left of the tissues.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a credit card on the coffee table.

high_descs: Walk to the dresser on the other side of the room.
Grab a card from the dresser.
Walk around to the dining table on the left side.
Place the card in a bowl.
Grab the bowl with the card.
Go to the coffee table in front of the sofa.
Place the bowl in the middle of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a card in a bowl and move them to the coffee table.

high_descs: Go to the lamp table
Pick up a credit card from the table
Go to the large main table
Put the credit card in a bowl on the large main table
Pick up the bowl with the credit card in it
Move to the glass table
Put the bowl on the glass table
anns.task_desc: Move a credit card and bowl to a different table
